---
// Leave Room Confirmation Modal
---

<div id="leave-modal" class="hidden fixed inset-0 bg-black/50 flex items-center justify-center z-50 modal-backdrop">
  <div class="bg-slate-800 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-slate-700 w-full max-w-sm mx-4 modal-content">
    <h2 class="text-xl font-semibold text-white mb-2">Leave Room?</h2>
    <p class="text-slate-400 mb-6">You'll need to rejoin with your name if you want to come back.</p>
    <div class="flex gap-3">
      <button
        id="cancel-leave-btn"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-600 text-white font-medium rounded-xl transition-colors btn-press"
      >
        Stay
      </button>
      <button
        id="confirm-leave-btn"
        class="flex-1 px-4 py-3 bg-red-600 hover:bg-red-500 text-white font-medium rounded-xl transition-colors btn-press"
      >
        Leave
      </button>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
